<br>
We had a deal. Your "I gave you all the time to convince me" line is a very poor cop-out. FYI: I don't come online to convince others I'm town. I'm here to hunt scum.

@Ircher - Kain would probably vote you too, so that's 6 right there. <br>
<br>
Why do you think Pop is scum, Irch? I'm not disagreeing or anything, just want to see your side?

