<br>
@Ircher - I liked your play at the end of this day, don't fail me.<br>
<br>
@Kain - oh, you are limited, which MAKES EVEN MORE SENSE than just gunsmith. Ha.<br>
<br>
@TTH - Jail me; I won't shoot tonight.

I'm done speaking for the day. Hammer away; if anyone else wants to say anything, speak up. <br>
